room_title: Escape room "The Emoryville Carnival" by Bakersfield Breakout Zone in Bakersfield
room_description: The town of Emeryville is being attacked by killer clowns! They have killed the detective and now have split your group up into two. Half of you are trapped in the detective's office, and half in a carnival tent. They have granted you 45 minutes to play their crazy games and try to escape. Will you escape or will you become the next victim of the clowns?
